data.description: This home is currently listed as a delayed showing. Under no circumstances will any showings be allowed until 4/20/21 at 10am. The Sellers will not review or accept any proposed Purchase Agreements/Offers until the conclusion of the first showing date. Looking for a great starter home? Are you a first time buyer? Do you have a small family? Look no further. This spacious 2 story home is just what you have been looking for. This 2 bedroom home has plenty of space to entertain on the main floor with a large dining room and living room. The huge kitchen is perfect for anyone that likes to cook.
